# Syncthing + vaultsync-notify
# Public domain: syncthing.example.com

# Syncthing API key — found in Syncthing's Settings -> GUI -> API Key.
# vaultsync-notify uses it to subscribe to FolderCompletion events and push
# debounced "vault changed" pings to the iOS VaultSync companion via the
# relay. Treat it like a password.
SYNCTHING_API_KEY=                       # generate via Syncthing UI, or: openssl rand -hex 16
